e Normans. In the later Middle Ages it was overtaken by   John  , but continued to run second to that name until the 20th century, when the picture became more fragmented."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"When Guillaume De Chartres IV Le Troubadour was born after 1215, in Chartres, Eure-et-Loir, France, his father, Geoffroy De Meslay, was 8819 and his mother, Hélissende De Ferrières, was 8810. He had at least 1 son with Jeanne De Bérou. He died in 1249."},"et":{"Aft 1215–1249":"pärast 1215–1249","1215–1249":"1215–1249","1225–Female":"1225–Surnud","1245–1321":"1245–1321","1180–1245":"1180–1245","1190–1251":"1190–1251","1190":"1190","1249":"1249","Aft 1215":"pärast 1215","1215":"1215","1225":"1225","Abt 1245":"umbes 1245","1245":"1245","1321":"1321","Abt 1215":"umbes 1215","1251":"1251","1180":"1180","Chartres, Eure-et-Loir, Centre-Val de Loire, France":"Chartres, Eure-et-Loir, Prantsusmaa","Meslay, Vendôme, Loir-et-Cher, Centre-Val de Loire, France":"Meslay, Loir-et-Cher, Centre, Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"Aft 1215–1249":"1215 jälkeen–1249","1215–1249":"1215–1249","1225–Female":"1225–Kuollut","1245–1321":"1245–1321","1180–1245":"1180–1245","1190–1251":"1190–1251","1190":"1190","1249":"1249","Aft 1215":"1215 jälkeen","1215":"1215","1225":"1225","Abt 1245":"noin 1245","1245":"1245","1321":"1321","Abt 1215":"noin 1215","1251":"1251","1180":"1180","Chartres, Eure-et-Loir, Centre-Val de Loire, France":"Chartres, Eure-et-Loir, Ranska","Meslay, Vendôme, Loir-et-Cher, Centre-Val de Loire, France":"Meslay, Loir-et-Cher, Centre, Ranska"},"fr":{"Aft 1215–1249":"après 1215–1249","1215–1249":"1215–1249","1225–Female":"1225–Décédée","1245–1321":"1245–1321","1180–1245":"1180–1245","1190–1251":"1190–1251","1190":"1190","1249":"1249","Aft 1215":"après 1215","1215":"1215","1225":"1225","Abt 1245":"environ 1245","1245":"1245","1321":"1321","Abt 1215":"environ 1215","1251":"1251","1180":"1180","Chartres, Eure-et-Loir, Centre-Val de Loire, France":"Chartres, Eure-et-Loir, France","Meslay, Vendôme, Loir-et